Emmerdale star Rebecca Sarker, who is best known for her role as Manpreet Sharma on the ITV soap, put on a busty display during her attendance at Soccer Aid 2022. Taking to Instagram today, the soap star shared a photo of her attire at the charity event as she rocked a red crop top with a plunging neckline, which gave a glimpse of her cleavage. The stylish star also unveiled her taut abs as the natural-faced beauty flashed the flesh. In view of her 42,600 followers, she captioned the post: "The beautiful game... Thank you to all who donated. Lovely to talk to you." Fans inundated the comment section, as Mike wrote: "Natural beauty. Gorgeous lady." Chloe Dooley commented: "So beautiful," while David added: "Gorgeous."